  "code_review": {
    "status": "pass",
    "findings_fixed": [
      "smoltcp is constrained to net_stack_adapter and target_executor orchestration; semantic_core stores only stable NetworkStackAdapter evidence",
      "NetworkStackAdapter requires exact PacketDevice, RxQueue, TxQueue, and backend generations",
      "Adapter binding validates the PacketDevice contract against adapter evidence, including MAC, MTU, queue depth, and payload size",
      "Socket capacity is explicitly zero so N10 cannot accidentally become the N11 SocketObject contract",
      "Duplicate adapter binding for one PacketDevice generation is rejected and command-visible",
      "The adapter builder returns Result on invalid contract/prefix/install paths and avoids production panic/expect paths"
    ],
